OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham has
OL,7,Funveiled his first cabinet, appointing
OL,8,FJohn Healey as chancellor and Angela
OL,9,FRayner as housing secretary, while
OL,10,Fremoving several allies of his
OL,11,Fpredecessor, Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,13,FAmong those leaving government are
OL,14,Fformer chancellor Rachel Reeves,
OL,15,Fformer foreign secretary David Lammy
OL,16,Fand former business secretary Peter
OL,17,FKyle, as Burnham reshaped the
OL,18,Fgovernment with allies in key posts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
