OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FOn his first day in office, Burnham
OL,7,Fannounced plans to scrap VAT on
OL,8,Fdomestic electricity bills from
OL,9,FOctober 1.
OL,11,FHe also pledged to end rough sleeping
OL,12,Fin his first speech, and said he
OL,13,Fwanted to deliver "a new political
OL,14,Fmodel and a new economic model" to
OL,15,Ftackle the cost-of-living crisis.
OL,17,FWith a significant workload awaiting
OL,18,Fthe new administration, ITV News takes
OL,19,Fa look at Burnham's cabinet
OL,20,Fappointments so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
