OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FJohn Healey ` Chancellor
OL,8,FA stalwart of Labour's frontbench,
OL,9,FHealey served in the Blair-Brown
OL,10,Fgovernments, as well as in the shadow
OL,11,Fcabinets of Ed Miliband and Jeremy
OL,12,FCorbyn.
OL,14,FHe then became Starmer's shadow
OL,15,Fdefence secretary, and then defence
OL,16,Fsecretary after the 2024 general
OL,17,Felection.
OL,19,FHealey now finds himself leading the
OL,20,FTreasury, a department which provoked
OL,21,Fhis exit from government in June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
