PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FHis shock resignation as defence
OL,7,Fsecretary came after a row about
OL,8,Fincreasing defence spending.
OL,10,FThat proved a significant moment in
OL,11,FStarmer's downfall as premier.
OL,13,FA source in Burnham's new ministry
OL,14,Fsaid Healey had been appointed because
OL,15,Fhe is a trusted and experienced figure
OL,16,Fwithin Labour, who shares the same
OL,17,Foutlook as the new prime minister.
OL,19,FEd Miliband ` Foreign Secretary
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
