PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FMiliband, who was dubbed "Red Ed" by
OL,7,Fthe tabloids during his time as Labour
OL,8,Fleader and was the subject of infamous
OL,9,Fphotographs of him eating a bacon
OL,10,Fsandwich during the 2015 general
OL,11,Felection campaign, returned to
OL,12,Ffrontline politics after the Corbyn
OL,13,Fera.
OL,15,FSince Labour's 2024 election victory,
OL,16,Fhe served as Energy Secretary in Keir
OL,17,FStarmer's government, leading its net
OL,18,Fzero agenda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
