CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FHe now becomes foreign secretary,
OL,7,Ftaking on the role of Britain's chief
OL,8,Fdiplomat.
OL,10,FA source close to Burnham said
OL,11,FMiliband was chosen because of his
OL,12,Fexperience on the international stage,
OL,13,Fincluding negotiating with governments
OL,14,Faround the world during his time as
OL,15,Fenergy secretary.
OL,17,FShabana Mahmood ` Home Secretary
OL,19,FMahmood remains as home secretary
OL,20,Funder Burnham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
