OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FIn her role, she led the government's
OL,7,Fwork on creating stricter migration
OL,8,Fcontrols.
OL,10,FAs Labour's efforts to tackle smuggler
OL,11,Fgangs have borne fruit in reducing
OL,12,FChannel crossings, calls from
OL,13,Fbackbench Labour MPs to soften new
OL,14,Fmigration curbs could prove an early
OL,15,Fflashpoint for Mahmood and Burnham.
OL,17,FOxford-educated former barrister,
OL,18,FMahmood served as justice secretary
OL,19,Fwhen Labour first won power, before
OL,20,Fshe was appointed home secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
