OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FShe is one of the first Muslim women
OL,7,Felected to the Commons, having won the
OL,8,Fseat of Birmingham Ladywood in 2010.
OL,10,FLouise Haigh ` Chancellor of the Duchy
OL,11,Fof Lancaster, and First Secretary of
OL,12,FState
OL,14,FLouise Haigh emerged as a key figure
OL,15,Fin Burnham's return to Westminster and
OL,16,Fhis successful bid for Downing Street,
OL,17,Fand was described as part of a group
OL,18,Fof "northern power women" who helped
OL,19,Fmastermind his Makerfield by-election
OL,20,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FHaigh previously criticised what she
OL,7,Fdescribed as a "boys' club" culture at
OL,8,Fthe heart of Starmer's Downing Street
OL,9,Foperation after she resigned as
OL,10,Ftransport secretary over a historic
OL,11,Fcriminal offence relating to
OL,12,Fincorrectly telling police in 2013
OL,13,Fthat a work mobile phone had been
OL,14,Fstolen.
OL,16,FAs Cabinet Office minister, Haigh is
OL,17,Fexpected to play a central role in
OL,18,Fdriving Burnham's priorities across
OL,19,FWhitehall, including his devolution
OL,20,Fagenda and plans to tackle the cost of
OL,21,Fliving crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
