OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FYvette Cooper ` Health Secretary
OL,8,FCooper, who served as home secretary
OL,9,Fand later foreign secretary in
OL,10,FStarmer's government, has been
OL,11,Fappointed health and social care
OL,12,Fsecretary in what some Westminster
OL,13,Fwatchers see as a demotion from one of
OL,14,Fthe four great offices of state.
OL,16,FA prominent figure in the New Labour
OL,17,Fera, Cooper served in the Blair and
OL,18,FBrown governments alongside Burnham
OL,19,Fbefore returning to the backbenches
OL,20,Fduring Jeremy Corbyn's leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
