CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FShe has now been tasked with
OL,7,Foverhauling England's social care
OL,8,Fsystem, a policy area Burnham has
OL,9,Fidentified as one of his top
OL,10,Fpriorities as prime minister.
OL,12,FWes Streeting - Defence Secretary
OL,14,FWes Streeting, who has been appointed
OL,15,Fas defence secretary, was initially
OL,16,Fseen as Burnham's main potential rival
OL,17,Fbut ruled himself out of the Labour
OL,18,Fleadership contest shortly after
OL,19,FStarmer announced his resignation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
