OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FHe had previously repeatedly insisted
OL,7,Fhe had the 81 names required to mount
OL,8,Fa leadership bid, and spent weeks
OL,9,Fafter resigning from Government
OL,10,Fsetting out his stall.
OL,12,FAngela Rayner ` Housing Secretary
OL,14,FAngela Rayner, once dubbed Labour's
OL,15,F"Red Queen", returns to the front line
OL,16,Fof government as housing secretary
OL,17,Fafter resigning from the same role in
OL,18,FStarmer's Cabinet, as well as stepping
OL,19,Fdown as Labour deputy leader and
OL,20,Fdeputy prime minister, over questions
OL,21,Fsurrounding her tax affairs last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FThe Ashton-under-Lyne MP was later
OL,7,Fcleared of any wrongdoing by HMRC.
OL,9,FRayner was seen meeting with Burnham
OL,10,Fin Greater Manchester earlier this
OL,11,Fyear, signalling her support for his
OL,12,Fbid to become Labour leader and prime
OL,13,Fminister.
OL,15,FA self-described socialist, Rayner
OL,16,Fpreviously championed Labour's
OL,17,Fworkers' rights agenda during her time
OL,18,Fin government and is now expected to
OL,19,Ffocus on tackling the housing crisis
OL,20,Fin her new role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
