OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FPat McFadden ` Work and Pensions
OL,7,FSecretary
OL,9,FVeteran frontbencher McFadden remains
OL,10,Fin his ministerial post overseeing
OL,11,Fwelfare spending and the state pension.
OL,13,FHe was widely seen as loyal to
OL,14,FStarmer, and was at times described as
OL,15,F"the real deputy prime minister" in
OL,16,Fhis time as Chancellor of the Duchy of
OL,17,FLancaster.
OL,19,FJonathan Reynolds ` Business Secretary
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/26
