OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FReynolds returns to the role of
OL,7,Fbusiness secretary, a role he held
OL,8,Fwhen Labour first came to power,
OL,9,Fbefore he was moved sideways to become
OL,10,Fthe party's chief whip.
OL,12,FThe role appears to have been
OL,13,Fsignificantly beefed up since he first
OL,14,Fheld it, and now covers science and
OL,15,Ftechnology as well.
OL,17,FLucy Powell ` Education Secretary
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
