OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784634473
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FAlex Norris, who has been appointed as
OL,7,FJustice Secretary, previously served
OL,8,Fas Minister of State for Border
OL,9,FSecurity and Asylum.
OL,11,FEarlier this month, Norris said "all
OL,12,Foptions are on the table" regarding
OL,13,Fthe deportation of Rochdale grooming
OL,14,Fgang leader Shabir Ahmed, who was
OL,15,Freleased from prison.
OL,17,FDame Angela Eagle ` Environment
OL,18,FSecretary
OL,26,@sD@aOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/26
