OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FDame Angela served as Minister of
OL,7,FState for Pensions and Ageing Society
OL,8,Ffrom June 2009 until May 2010 under
OL,9,FGordon Brown.
OL,11,FShe announced a leadership challenge
OL,12,Fto Jeremy Corbyn in July 2016, but
OL,13,Fwithdrew eight days later, leaving
OL,14,FOwen Smith to challenge Corbyn for the
OL,15,Fleadership.
OL,17,FMiatta Fahnbulleh ` Energy Secretary
