OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FMiatta Fahnbulleh, who resigned as a
OL,7,Fhousing minister in protest at
OL,8,FStarmer's leadership earlier this
OL,9,Fyear, has been advising Burnham and
OL,10,Ffleshing out his policy plans.
OL,12,FFahnbulleh, the new energy secretary,
OL,13,Fis considered to be a member of
OL,14,FBurnham's inner circle.
OL,16,FEllie Reeves ` Attorney General
OL,18,FEllie Reeves, sister of former
OL,19,Fchancellor Rachel Reeves, has served
OL,20,Fas solicitor general since September
OL,21,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/26
