OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FHeidi Alexander ` Transport Secretary
OL,8,FSwindon South MP Heidi Alexander will
OL,9,Fremain transport secretary, a post she
OL,10,Fhas held since November 2024.
OL,12,FShe previously served alongside
OL,13,FBurnham in Miliband's shadow cabinet
OL,14,Fbefore being appointed shadow health
OL,15,Fsecretary by Corbyn in 2015.
