OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FDouglas Alexander ` Secretary of State
OL,7,Ffor Scotland
OL,9,FDouglas Alexander, who has been
OL,10,Freappointed as Secretary of State for
OL,11,FScotland, previously served as
OL,12,FChancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster,
OL,13,FTransport Secretary and International
OL,14,FDevelopment Secretary in the cabinets
OL,15,Fof Tony Blair and Gordon Brown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/26
