OL,3,CAndy Burnham's cabinet: Who's in and
OL,4,Cwho's out?
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,7,Fsaid on Monday that relations with
OL,8,FWestminster had deteriorated over the
OL,9,Flast year as he signalled he did not
OL,10,Fwant Alexander to return as Scottish
OL,11,FSecretary in Burnham's Government.
OL,13,FStephen Kinnock ` Wales Secretary
OL,15,FStephen Kinnock will replace Jo
OL,16,FStevens as Welsh Secretary after two
OL,17,Fyears in the role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/26
